# ================================================================================
# HOW TO GET A SENDGRID API KEY:
# ================================================================================
# 1. Go to https://signup.sendgrid.com/ and create a free account
# 2. Verify your email address
# 3. Go to Settings > API Keys
# 4. Click "Create API Key"
# 5. Name it "ParcelReach Production"
# 6. Select "Full Access" permissions
# 7. Copy the API key (you won't be able to see it again!)
# 8. Paste it above as SENDGRID_API_KEY
#
# 9. IMPORTANT: Verify your sender email
#    - Go to Settings > Sender Authentication
#    - Click "Verify a Single Sender"
#    - Enter noreply@parcelreach.ai (or whatever email you want to use)
#    - Follow the verification process
#    - Update SENDGRID_FROM_EMAIL above with the verified email
#
# 10. Deploy to Netlify:
#    - Go to https://app.netlify.com/
#    - Select your ParcelReach site
#    - Go to Site configuration > Environment variables
#    - Add SENDGRID_API_KEY and SENDGRID_FROM_EMAIL
#    - Redeploy your site
# ================================================================================
